<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    {{> head title="Courses & Treatments for Companies"}}
    <link rel="canonical" hreflang="en" href="{{base_address}}/en/courses-company.html" />
</head>

<body>
    <main id="main">
        {{> header}}
        <section id="mainSection">
            {{> navEN langLink="/courses-company.html"}}
            </div>
            <div id="content">
                <!-- Insert content below -->

                <div class="textImgDiv">
                    <div class="textImgTxt">
                        <h3>Ayurveda for Health and Wellbeing in Your Organisation</h3>
                        <p>Ayurveda, the world's oldest health system, offers natural methods to promote health
                            and balance – fully in harmony with modern science. Bring these methods into your
                            organisation to create a workplace characterised by vitality, wellbeing and joy.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h2>Examples of Programme Options (we can also tailor a programme to your specific needs.)</h2>

                <div class="textImgDiv">
                    <img class="bigImg" src="/img/for-companies/presentation.jpg" alt="Presentation">
                    <div class="textImgTxt">
                        <h3>Workshop</h3>
                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Workshop on Ayurveda with a customised theme</span>
                            <span class="time">3 h</span>
                            <span class="type">group</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Price example for 20 participants: 12,000 SEK + VAT.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="textImgDiv">
                    <img class="bigImg" src="/img/for-companies/nurses-meditating.jpg" alt="Nurses meditating">
                    <div class="textImgTxt">
                        <h3>Consciousness development with Transcendental Meditation</h3>
                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Introductory workshop on consciousness</span>
                            <span class="time">1.5 h</span>
                            <span class="type">group</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Personal instruction</span>
                            <span class="time">1.5 h</span>
                            <span class="type">individual</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Four follow-up workshops</span>
                            <span class="time">3×1.5 h</span>
                            <span class="type">group</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Individual follow-up</span>
                            <span class="time">1 h</span>
                            <span class="type">individual</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Yoga and deepening retreat</span>
                            <span class="time">full-day</span>
                            <span class="type">group</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Price example for 10 participants: 87,000 SEK + VAT.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="textImgDiv">
                    <img class="bigImg" src="/img/for-companies/corporate-wellness.jpg" alt="Corporate wellness">
                    <div class="textImgTxt">
                        <h3>Ayurveda wellness programme</h3>
                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Introductory workshop on Ayurveda</span>
                            <span class="time">2 h</span>
                            <span class="type">group</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Personal health consultation</span>
                            <span class="time">1 h</span>
                            <span class="type">individual</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Two marma massage sessions</span>
                            <span class="time">2×1 h</span>
                            <span class="type">individual</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Yoga and Ayurvedic treatment retreat</span>
                            <span class="time">full-day</span>
                            <span class="type">group</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Price example for 10 participants: 48,000 SEK + VAT.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="textImgDiv">
                    <img class="bigImg" src="/img/for-companies/corporate-fitness.jpg" alt="Corporate fitness">
                    <div class="textImgTxt">
                        <h3>Ayurveda fitness programme</h3>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Introductory workshop on Ayurveda and training</span>
                            <span class="time">3 h</span>
                            <span class="type">group</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Personal health consultation with tailored training programme</span>
                            <span class="time">1 h</span>
                            <span class="type">individual</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Two marma massage sessions</span>
                            <span class="time">2×1 h</span>
                            <span class="type">individual</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Classical massage</span>
                            <span class="time">1 h</span>
                            <span class="type">individual</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Yoga and Ayurvedic treatment retreat</span>
                            <span class="time">full-day</span>
                            <span class="type">group</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="textRow">
                            <span class="text">Yoga and fitness retreat</span>
                            <span class="time">full-day</span>
                            <span class="type">group</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Price example for 10 participants: 75,000 SEK + VAT.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="textImgDiv">
                    <div class="textImgTxt">
                        <p>All programmes are led by Yvonne and Stefan Lagrosen, both university professors
                            specialising in workplace health with long-standing experience of working with
                            organisations. They are also trained in Yoga, Ayurveda and Transcendental Meditation.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <div id="darkFilter" onclick="toggleSmallScreenMenu()"></div>
    {{> scripts}}
</body>

</html>